User Stories: 

As a reader, I want to be able to view blog posts. 
As a reader, I want to be able to search blog posts. 
As a reader, I would like to be able to click on a tag to view other posts with the same tag. 
As a reader, I would like to be able to add comments. 

As an admin/user, I would like to be able to create a new post.
As an admin/user, I would like to be able to edit a post.
As an admin/user(?), I would like to be able to delete a post.

As an admin/user(?), I would like to be able to create a new static page.
As an admin/user(?), I would like to be able to edit a new static page.
As an admin/user(?), I would like to be able to delete a static page.

As an admin, I would like to be able to approve posts.
As an admin, I would like to be able to approve edits.
As an admin, I would like to be able to approve comments.
